{"tid":2293552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果：副廣播處長馮建業為調查利君雅 要求IT部係傳訊組同事不在公司下 解鎖同事的電腦及電郵","createTime":"2020-11-20T10:12:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T10:39:29.000Z","uid":22556,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b51f518acc7d2d2674c6bc87656d90f2fbdaebad","tid":2293552,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T10:12:24.000Z","msg":"香港電台助理節目主任利君雅被延長試用期及重啟調查，事件餘波未了。《蘋果》獲悉，負責重啟調查的副廣播處長馮建業，疑下令IT部，「鬼祟」解鎖檢閱機構傳訊及節目標準組員工的電腦和工作電郵，聲稱要查閱之前涉利君雅的投訴。<br />\n<br />\n據悉有傳訊組員工更表明「一日佢喺位，都唔可以咁樣夾硬嚟」，惟管方最終上周出動IT部員工，趁傳訊組同事不在時，將其電腦及工作電郵解鎖檢閱，被解鎖電腦的包括部門主管級人員。但暫未確認牽涉多少名員工的電腦和電郵、亦未知多少和有何資料被查閱。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201120/DLSJJ6IN4RHZ7HO2KHCLGBUNXQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201120%2FDLSJJ6IN4RHZ7HO2KHCLGBUNXQ%2F&d=gxBKi3yaaNwv0eARaXv6BWZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=00783df0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201120%2FDLSJJ6IN4RHZ7HO2KHCLGBUNXQ%2F&h=1afda746\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201120/DLSJJ6IN4RHZ7HO2KHCLGBUNXQ/</a>"},{"pid":"e460f48efa959160115f36b66b59811ca4b9916e","tid":2293552,"uid":383914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T10:14:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連豬偷睇到資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ded8e0783a76cf452cec674e389bf8add182c39","tid":2293552,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T10:15:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86637c2ce28c0ad9415683e9e4099337d090d429","tid":2293552,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply